metadata.description: SAEKKO & Risto join together to create a beautiful artistically crafted, passionate and emotive alt-rock track: Lucid Dream. We hope you enjoy listening to it, as much as we enjoyed creating it. This song is showered in the themes of love; true love, and all of the feelings that come along with it. Love can sometimes seem like that of a dream; an unexplainable occurrence and phenomenon only two united souls can attempt to make sense of. When love does happen, it is Amazing â€¦ Enjoy! Yours Truly, SAEKKO x Risto
metadata.name: SAEKKO & RISTO - Lucid Dream
